com.atakmap.android.bloodhound.util

Class BloodHoundToolLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.bloodhound.util.BloodHoundToolLink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MapItem.OnGroupChangedListener, MapItem.OnVisibleChangedListener

    public class BloodHoundToolLink
extends java.lang.Object
implements MapItem.OnGroupChangedListener, MapItem.OnVisibleChangedListener
    This class handles the behavior of the bloodhound link managed by the bloodhound tool. This is in contrast to BloodHoundLink, which handles bloodhound links which were created by selecting the bloodhound button in the radial menu for range and bearing lines. Currently, this class has the capability to be in "R&B line mode", or "route mode", whereas a BloodHoundLink is always an R&B line.
